s.\" width=\"2976\" height=\"2458\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.68deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2976×2458\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Chat interface showing conversation with AI about building an Electron desktop app, with console errors displaying Content Security Policy violations.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Developer workspace showing Vuepecula chat application with commit history, source control changes, TypeScript component errors, and testing checklist for UI/UX improvements.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1740253623/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.53_PM.png\" alt=\"Developer workspace showing Vuepecula chat application with commit history, source control changes, TypeScript component errors, and testing checklist for UI/UX improvements.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1740253623/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.53_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1740253623/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.53_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1740253623/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.53_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1740253623/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.53_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Developer workspace showing Vuepecula chat application with commit history, source control changes, TypeScript component errors, and testing checklist for UI/UX improvements.\" width=\"3600\" height=\"2338\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.86deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3600×2338\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Developer workspace showing Vuepecula chat application with commit history, source control changes, TypeScript component errors, and testing checklist for UI/UX improvements.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Vulpecula chat interface showing two conversation sessions with R1 1776 model, displaying message counts, timestamps, token usage, and cost metrics.\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1740253625/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.56_PM.png\" alt=\"Vulpecula chat interface showing two conversation sessions with R1 1776 model, displaying message counts, timestamps, token usage, and cost metrics.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1740253625/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.56_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1740253625/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.56_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1740253625/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.56_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1740253625/Screenshot_2025-02-22_at_2.46.56_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Vulpecula chat interface showing two conversation sessions with R1 1776 model, displaying message counts, timestamps, token usage, and cost metrics.\" width=\"684\" height=\"816\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.8deg;\" data-dimensions=\"684×816\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-[3/4] w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Vulpecula chat interface showing two conversation sessions with R1 1776 model, displaying message counts, timestamps, token usage, and cost metrics.</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Vulpecula chat interface showing two conversation sessions with R